SYNOPSIS

     use Log::ger::Format 'Sprintfn';
     use Log::ger;

    After that:

     log_debug 'user is %(username)s, details are %(detail)s',
         {username=>"Foo", detail=>{...}};

    To install only for current package:

     use Log::ger::Format;
     Log::ger::Format->set_for_current_package('Sprintfn');
     use Log::ger;

DESCRIPTION

SEE ALSO

    Log::ger

    Text::sprintfn

